"No. See, that's me. That's me."

1611
02:18:42,204 --> 02:18:44,104
We stared at the two candles,

1612
02:18:44,206 --> 02:18:46,106
and then...

1613
02:18:47,409 --> 02:18:49,240
Well, if you remember
any of this,

1614
02:18:49,344 --> 02:18:51,744
I'm sure you remember
the next part.

1615
02:18:54,816 --> 02:18:58,217
But there are
two candles in the dark.

1616
02:18:59,621 --> 02:19:01,714
I'm with you.

1617
02:19:01,823 --> 02:19:04,792
I'll always be with you, Bud.
I promise that.

1618
02:19:18,206 --> 02:19:21,437
How you doin', partner?

1619
02:19:21,543 --> 02:19:24,444
You still with us?
Come back.

1620
02:19:24,546 --> 02:19:27,106
- You talk to us, Buddy boy.
- [Sobbing]

1621
02:19:27,215 --> 02:19:29,615
- Come on.
- Bud.

1622
02:19:29,718 --> 02:19:32,619
Bud? Now, come on.
You hangin' in there?

1623
02:19:33,989 --> 02:19:36,890
You have to talk to me, Bud.
Please.

1624
02:19:36,992 --> 02:19:38,459
I need to know
if you're okay.

1625
02:19:45,617 --> 02:19:47,915
[All Sighing]

1626
02:19:53,659 --> 02:19:56,025
<i>[Lindsey]
You see... You see a light?</i>

1627
02:19:56,128 --> 02:19:59,620
What kind of light, Bud?

1628
02:19:59,731 --> 02:20:02,632
He's hallucinating badly.

1629
02:20:23,655 --> 02:20:27,318
<i>- He made it.
- [Sighs] Oh, my God.</i>

1630
02:20:27,426 --> 02:20:29,326
Oh, man.

1631
02:20:30,729 --> 02:20:34,165
Okay, Bud,
we'll go step by step.

1632
02:20:34,266 --> 02:20:37,394
Remove the detonator housing...

1633
