All right, Bud,
you have to cut the ground wire,

1635
02:21:15,641 --> 02:21:17,973
not the lead wire.

1636
02:21:18,076 --> 02:21:20,169
It's the blue wire
with the white stripe.

1637
02:21:20,279 --> 02:21:22,679
<i>Not... I repeat...</i>

1638
02:21:22,781 --> 02:21:26,649
<i>not the black wire
with the yellow stripe.</i>

1639
02:21:43,902 --> 02:21:46,564
[All Sighing]

1640
02:22:20,639 --> 02:22:22,539
[All Cheering]

