- Yes!
- Quiet! Quiet. Save your air.

1642
02:22:25,577 --> 02:22:28,205
Bud, give me a reading
off your liquid oxygen gauge.

1643
02:22:35,787 --> 02:22:38,654
What?

1644
02:22:38,757 --> 02:22:41,954
- It took him 30 minutes
just to get down there!
- Bud, do you hear me?

1645
02:22:42,060 --> 02:22:45,962
You drop your weights and start back
now, Bud! That gauge could be wrong!

1646
02:22:46,064 --> 02:22:49,898
Do you hear me? Just drop
your weights and start back now.

1647
02:22:50,001 --> 02:22:53,198
Your gauge could be wrong!
Your gauge could be wrong!

1648
02:22:53,305 --> 02:22:56,274
You drop your weights
and start back now!

1649
02:22:59,378 --> 02:23:02,609
<i>No, you won't stay there!
Do you hear me? You drop your weights.</i>

1650
02:23:02,714 --> 02:23:05,205
You can breathe shallow!
Do you hear me?

1651
02:23:05,317 --> 02:23:08,184
Bud, please! Listen to me,
please! Goddamn it!

1652
02:23:08,286 --> 02:23:12,848
You dragged me
back from the bottomless pit!
You can't leave me here alone now!

1653
02:23:12,958 --> 02:23:16,587
Please.
Oh, God, Virgil, please.

1654
02:23:16,695 --> 02:23:19,095
Please.

1655
02:23:59,771 --> 02:24:01,705
I love you.

1656
02:28:14,125 --> 02:28:17,686
[Inhaling Deeply]

1657
02:29:00,187 --> 02:29:02,587
[Coughing]

1658
02:29:07,662 --> 02:29:09,653
Howdy.

1659
02:29:09,764 --> 02:29:12,756
Uh, how you guys doin'?

1660
02:29:17,738 --> 02:29:22,732
...attempts to convene a summit between
heads of state have collapsed...

1661
02:29:22,843 --> 02:29:25,903
Soviet buildup of tanks
and aircraft have...

1662
02:29:26,013 --> 02:29:30,245
<i>[Man #2] All citizens to stay on their
jobs, restrict unnecessary travel...</i>

1663
