- [Man #3] We had moments ago
an unprovoked attack...
- Holy shit.

1664
02:29:33,921 --> 02:29:37,550
Across the country, National Guard
units have been mobilized,

1665
02:29:37,658 --> 02:29:41,458
and also defense volunteer staff
have been called to full-time duty.

1666
02:29:44,498 --> 02:29:47,058
You watch our TV.
That's what you're tellin' me...

1667
02:29:47,168 --> 02:29:49,398
that you know what's
goin' on up there?

1668
02:29:49,503 --> 02:29:52,631
<i>Seismologists worldwide are reporting
an enormous disturbance...</i>

1669
02:29:52,740 --> 02:29:56,801
throughout the world's oceans which
apparently began about 15 minutes ago.

1670
02:29:56,911 --> 02:30:01,678
They are acoustic shock waves,
like tsunamis, but with no
apparent seismological source.

1671
02:30:01,782 --> 02:30:06,219
<i>The waves are propagating toward
the shorelines of every continent.</i>

1672
02:30:06,320 --> 02:30:08,948
[Woman] Dr. Berg, would you
please, based on the...

1673
02:30:09,056 --> 02:30:12,423
Young lady, listen to me.
We don't know what's going on yet.

1674
02:30:12,526 --> 02:30:15,893
<i>We don't have a clue.</i>

1675
02:30:15,996 --> 02:30:18,089
The horizon has already
grown dark.

1676
02:30:18,199 --> 02:30:21,430
People are running everywhere.
It's... It's sheer panic.

1677
02:30:21,535 --> 02:30:27,030
Stay on me! The wave... The wave
is maybe 1,000 feet high already.

1678
02:30:27,141 --> 02:30:29,234
<i>Getting bigger
as I'm watching.</i>

1679
02:30:29,343 --> 02:30:33,211
Still miles out.
Oh, my God.

1680
02:30:33,314 --> 02:30:35,578
- We're out of here.
- We're staying!

1681
02:30:35,683 --> 02:30:39,449
Give us a minute. I don't even know
if I'm still broadcasting.

1682
02:30:39,553 --> 02:30:43,489
I can't be sure.
I'll just keep going as long as I can.

1683
02:30:43,591 --> 02:30:46,025
- Get out of the way!
- A thousand...

