You guys are doing this, right?
You can control water.

1686
02:30:55,503 --> 02:30:58,836
That's your technology.
But why are you doin' this?

1687
02:30:59,940 --> 02:31:03,103
[Loud Hum Resonating]

1688
02:31:16,290 --> 02:31:18,850
Okay.

1689
02:31:18,959 --> 02:31:21,985
Okay, that's enough.
I get the point!

1690
02:31:23,430 --> 02:31:28,231
How do you know that
they're really gonna do it?

1691
02:31:28,335 --> 02:31:32,772
Where do you get off passin'
judgment on us? You can't be sure.

1692
02:31:32,873 --> 02:31:34,773
How do you know?

1693
02:32:18,285 --> 02:32:20,583
[Horns Honking]

1694
02:32:20,688 --> 02:32:24,055
[People Shouting, Screaming]

1695
02:32:40,341 --> 02:32:42,673
<i>[Man Speaking Russian Over P.A.]</i>

1696
02:32:42,776 --> 02:32:45,677
<i>[Alarm Blaring]</i>

1697
02:34:29,783 --> 02:34:32,343
