1703
02:36:07,247 --> 02:36:12,275
<i>[Faintly] Deep Core, do you read?
This is Benthic Explorer. Over.</i>

1704
02:36:12,386 --> 02:36:14,877
Hell, yes, we read.
Good of you to join us.

1705
02:36:14,988 --> 02:36:19,357
- Copy, Deep Core. Hey, I've got 'em!
- How's that storm up there?

1706
02:36:19,460 --> 02:36:22,258
It's strange. It just blew
itself out all of a sudden.

1707
02:36:22,362 --> 02:36:25,729
Hell, son, you better get
a line down to us.

1708
02:36:25,833 --> 02:36:30,202
<i>We're in moderately
